public class SunJrmpExporter
extends Object
implements net.jini.export.Exporter
    JRMP exporter to export an object using a well-known object identifier. This exporter implementation is only designed to work with Java(TM) 2 Standard Edition implementations from Sun Microsystems(TM), Inc.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
